data.description: Location, location, location! This fabulous townhome is right in the middle of the 161, 114 & 183 corridor - you are just a stone throw away to all the entertainment you could want. Home is currently vacant, but just take a look at the pictures to see all the amazing potential. This beautifully-maintained gated community features a neighborhood swimming pool. BRAND NEW outside & inside HVAC units for the upstairs! The monthly HOA includes yard service to your front AND back yards, as well as exterior maintenance including the roof. To sweeten the deal, the owner is including the fridge, washer and dryer with the sale of the home. This seller is motivated, so bring your offers!
